A Kenyan police officer was killed
and three others were injured when a grenade exploded a vehicle
in the capital, Nairobi,  Capital FM  said.  The explosion took place today as people were searching for
a device that had been thrown into a police vehicle on a busy
street in the Eastleigh suburb, the Nairobi radio station
reported, citing unidentified police officials.  Kenyan police spokesman Eric Kiraithe didnâ€™t answer his
